<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>About Us - Blog Company</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    
    main {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .about-section {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    
    .about-image {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .about-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #333;
    }
    
    .about-description {
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #555;
    }
    
    /* Media Query for Responsive Design */
    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .about-image {
        width: 150px;
        height: 150px;
      }
      
      .about-title {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      
      .about-description {
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <section class="about-section">
      <img src="img/about.png" alt="Company Logo" class="about-image">
      <h2 class="about-title">About Us</h2>
      <p class="about-description">
        Welcome to our blog! Discover valuable insights, tips, and inspiration for bloggers. Our expert writers cover lifestyle, travel, tech, health, and more. Find practical advice on content creation, SEO, and social media. Explore our archives for in-depth guides and interviews. Engage with our community by leaving comments and sharing your thoughts. We value your feedback and suggestions. Join our mailing list for exclusive updates and content. Thank you for visiting - happy reading and happy blogging!
    </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
